5b7c1959a8a0ec0","tid":1683941,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHuaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=1d30f103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9caa1b4795533cbe84e3b9aeed344451aac51a4","tid":1683941,"uid":217415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91ef6d423ae66a065a49c504db5fd11650931127","tid":1683941,"uid":11447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:08:35.000Z","msg":"漆彈好似講左三個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"點解咁耐都無人用"},{"pid":"60f5b7de1d85fe647d64f08320fb516b1dc02d2f","tid":1683941,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"油漆彈槍犯唔犯法？"},{"pid":"2